BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:ZJrZ6ociChg3imfBjz3AQ
SUMMARY:PCC Cooking Class - Savory Sichuan
DTSTAMP:20260326T230622Z
DTSTART:20260329T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Learn to make traditional Chinese dishes at home! In this cooki
	ng class\, you’ll pick up techniques and tips for capturing the flavors of
	 Sichuan cuisine. Get practice infusing oil with chilis and hand-grinding 
	spices for a sauce as you create deeply flavorful dan dan noodles. You’ll 
	also try your hand at methodically rolling and flattening dough with scall
	ions for savory pancakes\, which you’ll pair with a scratch-made dipping s
	auce. By the end of class\, you’ll be ready to recreate the entire menu in
	 your kitchen. \n\nContains pork and dairy. \n\nAbout the instructor: Our 
	seasoned instructors and chefs have been chosen to be a part of PCC Cooks 
	because of their culinary expertise and sincere enthusiasm and talent for 
	teaching. \n\nThis is a hands-on format class for adults. \n\n This cookin
	g class is available at multiple PCC locations and dates. See below for de
	tails: \n\nBellevue PCC \n\n-Friday\, March 27\, 6:00 - 8:00 pm \n\n-Sunda
	y\, March 29\, 10:00 - 12:00 pm \n\n-Friday\, April 3\, 10:00 - 12:00 pm \
	n\nBothell PCC \n\n-Friday\, March 27\, 6:00 - 8:00 pm \n\n-Sunday\, March
	 29\, 10:00 - 12:00 pm \n\nBurien PCC \n\n-Sunday\, March 29\, 10:00 - 12:
	00 pm \n\nColumbia City PCC \n\n-Sunday\, March 29\, 10:00 - 12:00 pm \n\n
	Edmonds PCC \n\n-Friday\, March 27\, 6:00 - 8:00 pm \n\n-Sunday\, March 29
	\, 10:00 - 12:00 pm \n\nGreen Lake Village PCC \n\n-Friday\, March 27\, 6:
	00 - 8:00 pm \n\n-Sunday\, March 29\, 10:00 - 12:00 pm\n\nhttps://seatoday
	.6amcity.com/events/#/details/pcc-cooking-class-savory-sichuan/18296264/20
	26-03-29T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Food & Drink
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/pcc-cooking-class-savory-
	sichuan/18296264/2026-03-29T00
LOCATION:Columbia City PCC\, 3610 S Edmunds St\, Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-food
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Food & Drink
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:VtB9Y1fXWCa4ygKtERoJ9
SUMMARY:March Madness Watch Party at Five Iron Golf - Seattle Capitol Hill
DTSTAMP:20260326T230622Z
DTSTART:20260329T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Five Iron Golf is your College Basketball HQ this March! Gather
	 your crew and book 1–2 simulator bays for up to 12 people \\(6 people per
	 bay\\) for a bracket-busting watch party experience. Enjoy all-day TV cov
	erage of college basketball alongside cutting-edge golf and multisport sim
	ulators\, a locally-inspired menu\, and custom beverage packages.\n\nBook 
	your watch party for March 19 or 20 and you'll automatically be entered to
	 win a 20-person happy hour with drinks and appetizers — a $1\,000 value!\
	n\nGroup packages can include reserved event space\, team-specific décor\,
	 a dedicated staff member\, full-screen and/or picture-in-picture viewing\
	, a customizable menu\, beverage packages\, free club rentals\, multisport
	 simulators\, and table games. Select the "Small Event" option at booking 
	to ensure simulator bays are placed side-by-side. Availability of select f
	eatures varies by location.\n\nPromotions:\n\nHappy Hour – "It's 5i o'Cloc
	k Somewhere" \\(Monday–Friday\, 3–6 PM\\)\n\nEnjoy $5 bottomless boneless 
	wings\, $10 bottomless bone-in wings\, $5 select beers/cans/cocktails\, $5
	 dips \\(guacamole\, hot honey ricotta\, hummus\\)\, half-off pizzas\, and
	 $5 featured shots. Dine-in only at participating locations\; simulator re
	ntal may be required.\n\n5i After Dark – "Swing In\, For Less"  \\(Sunday–
	Thursday 9 PM to close | Friday–Saturday 10 PM to close\\)\n\nFeatures $29
	/hr simulator rentals plus the same great food and drink specials as Happy
	 Hour\, with wings priced per dozen rather than bottomless. Dine-in only a
	t participating locations\; simulator rental may be required.\n\nhttps://s
	eatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/march-madness-watch-party-at-five-iro
	n-golf-seattle-capitol-hill/18268907/2026-03-29T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Food
	 & Drink
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/march-madness-watch-party
	-at-five-iron-golf-seattle-capitol-hill/18268907/2026-03-29T00
LOCATION:Five Iron Golf - Seattle Capitol Hill\, 1525 11th Ave Suite 100\, 
	Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-food
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Food & Drink
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT12H
END:VEVENT
